                <p>
                    iLNB transceiver is an entry level product that significantly lowers the price of Kacific’s consumer-oriented
                    terminals without compromising performance.
                    It is capable of speeds of up to 50Mbps down and 10Mbps up, further reinforcing the total cost-effectiveness of the
                    Kacific broadband plans for consumer and SME end-users.
                </p>
                <h1 class="invisibleSpace"> &nbsp; </h1>
                <div class="inquireButtons">
                    <button class="inquire-btn">INQUIRE NOW</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
